OL,3,COne second glory for Belfast City
OL,4,CMarathon winner
OL,6,FThe pair fought hard to to the finish
OL,7,Fline with Mamo finishing in 2:16:24.
OL,9,FAziza Alaoui Selsouli came first in
OL,10,Fthe Women's Race in a time of 2:38:00.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Jayne Bleakley won the
OL,13,FWheelchair Race in a time of 2:32:39.
OL,15,FDrivers are advised of traffic
OL,16,Fdisruption around Belfast due to road
OL,17,Fclosures.
OL,19,FThey are expected to fully reopen at
OL,20,F4.30pm.
